      "title": "USPA Tested and Open 2026 Ironville Classic, Waynesville, Missouri",
      "description": "<div  class=\"tribe-events-schedule tribe-clearfix\" >\n\t<p class=\"tribe-events-schedule__datetime\">\n\t\t<span class=\"tribe-events-schedule__date tribe-events-schedule__date--start\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tribe-events-schedule__separator tribe-events-schedule__separator--date\">\n\t\t\t\t @ \t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"tribe-events-schedule__time tribe-events-schedule__time--start\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sanction#:</strong>&nbsp;26-45775</p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"block-17df44be-cda3-4c50-84b3-f63d16e8b9b9\"><strong>Limited to 60 lifters</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>This event has both Tested and Non Tested Divisions available</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"block-dc4ce0f7-79fe-4826-870b-57e2872e42bf\"><strong>Refund Policy:</strong>&nbsp;No refunds unless there is a paid lifter to take your spot. If you receive a refund, there will be a $25 processing fee subtracted from your entry fee. Entry fees are not transferable to another meet or person, and no refunds will be given after February 14, 2026.</p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"block-349c1fc4-4a89-47ae-be6b-c0aa23a7d177\"><strong>Registration closes:\u00a0</strong>February 27, 2026</p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"block-349c1fc4-4a89-47ae-be6b-c0aa23a7d177\"><strong>For the Tested Division:</strong>&nbsp;Drug testing by urinalysis. Drug Testing will be a 10% targeted random selection based on the top Dots scores.</p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"block-6b689fec-a6bb-4b4e-8d90-bd07053da7b3\"><strong>Events:&nbsp;</strong>Full Power, Bench Only, Deadlift Only, Push Pull<br><strong>Category:</strong>&nbsp;Raw, Classic Raw, Single Ply</p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"block-22ceb734-87f8-40a8-80b1-83196f319909\"><strong>Weigh in Schedule:</strong><br>Friday, March 13, 2026 \u2013 9:00 am to 11:00 am or 4:00 pm to 6:00 pm.<br>If we have not heard from you by 5pm on Friday, you will be removed from the meet.<br><em>No same day weigh-ins. NO EXCEPTIONS</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"block-22ceb734-87f8-40a8-80b1-83196f319909\"></p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"block-5afa34da-d0ef-48d2-94fb-203bc4bff8b5\"><strong>Event Schedule:</strong><br><strong>Warmup:</strong>&nbsp;8:00 am<br><strong>Lifting Begins:&nbsp;</strong>9:00 am</p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"block-965db4b0-dc7c-4193-bff1-87eca0f23a9f\"><strong>Awards:</strong><br><strong>Open:</strong>&nbsp;1st \u2013 3rd place in each weight class<br><strong>Junior 10-12, 13-15, 16-17, 18-19, 20-23:</strong>&nbsp;1st \u2013 3rd place in each weight class and age group<br><strong>Submaster 35-39:</strong>&nbsp;1st \u2013 3rd place in each weight class<br><strong>Master 40-44, 45-49, etc.:&nbsp;</strong>1st \u2013 3rd place in each weight class and age group.<br><strong>Best Lifter:</strong>&nbsp;Awards given to each qualified lifter with 5 or more competitors in their class.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bars that will be used on the platform will be Texas Squat Bar, Texas Powerbar, Texas Deadlift Bar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Qualifier For:</strong><br>Any IPL Competition or USPA National Level Competition with the necessary qualifying total during the appropriate qualifying period.</p>\n\n\n<div  class=\"tribe-block tribe-block__event-price\" >\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n<div  class=\"tribe-block tribe-block__organizer__details tribe-clearfix\" >\n\t<div class=\"tribe-block__organizer__title\">\n\t\t<h3><a href=\"https://uspa.net/organizer/frankie-murrieta-sheena-hodges/\" title=\"Frankie Murrieta &#038; Sheena Hodges\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"\">Frankie Murrieta &#038; Sheena Hodges</a></h3>\n\t</div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"tribe-block__organizer__phone\">808-779-9063</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"tribe-block__organizer__email\">fl&#119;p&#111;werl&#105;&#102;ti&#110;g&#064;&#103;m&#097;i&#108;&#046;com</p>\n\t</div>\n\n\n<div  class=\"tribe-block tribe-block__venue tribe-clearfix\" >\n\t\n\t\t\n\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t<div  class=\"tribe-block tribe-block__events-link\" >\n\t\t<div class=\"tribe-events tribe-common\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"tribe-events-c-subscribe-dr